<item>
            <title>[LU-1671] Remove duplicate data from (at least ZFS OSD) LDD</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1671</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ldd_fsname, ldd_svindex, and ldd_flags (LDD_F_SV_TYPE_XXX) contain duplicate data with ldd_svname.  The duplication should be removed, at least from the new ZFS OSD LDD, to avoid confusion.  I&apos;m not sure how difficult it will be for LDiskFS OSD, but for ZFS OSD, this should be straightforward before ZFS is officially supported.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
